advcalclib (1.0.0-1) jammy; urgency=medium

  * Initial release
  * Linear algebra support (2x2, 3x3, 4x4 matrices)
  * Statistical functions (variance, std dev, confidence intervals)
  * Calculus operations (derivatives, integrals)
  * Algebraic solvers (cubic equations, binomial expansion)
  * Cross-platform CMake build system

